items.title: How to turn off autoplay on your social media feeds
items.description: Here's how you can turn off autoplaying videos and GIFs on Facebook, Instagram, X, Twitter, and Threads.

items.title: While US stalls, Australia and Anduril move to put XL undersea vehicle into service
items.description: Anduril has landed a lucrative contract and is bringing its uncrewed undersea vehicle Ghost Shark to Australian waters next year.

items.title: Klarna’s IPO pops, raising $1.4B, with Sequoia as the biggest winner
items.description: Of the 34.3 million shares Klarna sold, only 5 million were sold by the company, it said. The rest were sold by existing investors.

items.title: OpenAI and Oracle reportedly ink historic cloud computing deal
items.description: OpenAI and Oracle reportedly signed a deal that includes OpenAI buying $300 billion of compute over a five-year span.

items.title: YouTube’s multi-language audio feature for dubbing videos rolls out to all creators
items.description: YouTube's multi-language audio feature is rolling out to millions of creators, helping them reach a wider global audience.
